*extensões que precisa baixar pra rodar o react-navigation*

npm install @react-navigation/native

npm install react-native-screens react-native-safe-area-context

*extensões que precisa para baixar pra rodar o DrawerNavigator*

npm install @react-navigation/drawer

npx expo install react-native-gesture-handler react-native-reanimated

npm install react-native-gesture-handler react-native-reanimated

*extensões que precisa para baixar pra rodar o Tab Navigator*

npm install @react-navigation/bottom-tabs

npm install @react-navigation/native-stack

npm install expo-status-bar

*para mais, acesse: https://reactnavigation.org/docs/getting-started*